flowRoot.flowPara: After graduating as BSc and working for IBM Germany I decided to move abroad in 2011. I arrived in London at Last.fm and have now moved on to work at Gamevy.
I spend a lot of my time walking around, listening to Science Fiction audio books (recommendations welcome!). You might find me in a pub or sometimes at London Hackspace. Why not get in touch?
